Cite this CHANGES
=================

Cite This 0.3.1 (2008-02-09T00:14:24+0800)
------------------------------------------
Added: Post status checking
Deled: `GetCTdynamicPath()`
Fixed: Author name doesn't show up, if no first name and last name settings.

Cite This 0.3.0.1 (2007-11-21T08:43:20+0800)
--------------------------------------------
Fixed: 5 - Deactivate Plugin not working.
Fixed: 6 - Reset All Options messes Citation Style up.
Moded: Change plugin name to 'Cite This'

Cite This 0.3 (2007-11-19T14:00:26+0800)
----------------------------------------
Moded: Using built-in (un)serialize mechanism for options.
Moded: Rewrite the text in Options Page.
Moded: Show widget in pages.
Fixed: Typo in option name `CTgerneralOptions`.

* The following issues were filed in old tracker of Google Code *

